manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: GIAOQ Multi-functional Smart Watches Classic circular design -- 1.32-inch HD touchscreen smartwatch with a thin metal frame. Bright and round full touch display, elegant watch face, bring more comfortable viewing experience. Receive/make calls - You can make and receive calls directly on your watch when connected to Bluetooth. GIAOQ smartwatch, with text and call function, support fast communication, Message Notifications - Turn on the message alerts on the APP and the smartwatch will sync your text messages and social media information (Facebook, WhatsApp, Instagram, Twitter, etc.). Supported operating systems -- iOS 10.0 or later, Android 5.0 or later, Bluetooth 5.0

DIY Smartwatch Dial 100 + Free Watch Faces: There are more than 100 free watch faces in the app for you to change. The dials are available in various styles to match the needs of people of different ages. DIY Dial: In addition, our smartwatch also supports custom watch faces, you can upload your favorite pictures as your watch faces, such as your family, pets, idols, etc. Tips：The watchfaces in the watch face store will be updated from time to time, and more surprises are waiting for you to discover!

Muti-Function Smartwatch IP67 Waterproof:1 meter deep, 30 minutes. The waterproof design is perfect for sports enthusiasts. You can wear this watch for daily hand-washing and rainy days. Note: Please do not use in diving, hot water or corrosive liquid and hot steam environment. Waterproofing is not permanent and protection may be reduced due to daily wear and tear. Multiple sport modes: As a fitness watch, our fitness tracker supports multiple exercise modes: walking, running, badminton, skipping, basketball, soccer, cycling, etc. Activity tracker: A personal fitness trainer on your wrist can use the fitness tracker to check your distance, speed, heart rate, calories consumed, etc., to help you record the data during exercise, so that you can live a healthy life and exercise more professionally. Sleep monitoring: Sleep tracker will automatically monitor sleep status from 9pm to 9am while wearing a watch and provide comprehensive analysis of sleep quality (deep sleep, light sleep and wake). The data will be recorded on the APP, and you can use the data to learn about your sleep quality and adjust your daily routine. 24/7 heart rate monitor: The heart rate monitor automatically monitors your heart rate throughout the day. Blood oxygen monitor: Using the latest photoelectric sensing technology, according to the principle that the amount of light absorbed by the artery blood changes with the pulse of the artery, optical measurement. The Exercise watch monitors blood oxygen saturation during periods of discomfort or high intensity exercise to instantly understand your physical condition and help you lead a healthier lifestyle. Blood pressure monitor: Smartwatch has blood pressure monitoring function.

How to connect smart watch? 1. Long press the side button of the watch for 3-5 seconds, turn it on, open the QR code on the setting page, scan the QR code to download the ‘RDFit ’APP. 2. Turn on the phone's Bluetooth and location services, and make sure that the smart watch is not bound to other phones. 3. Open the RDFit APP on the phone, set personal information, enter the device "interface", click "add device", swipe to the right on the main dial interface of the bracelet, you can view the Bluetooth MAC address of the bracelet, you can use the MAC in the device list Address to determine your device, select the searched device name and the corresponding MAC address, click pair, the bracelet is connected successfully. How do I use the call function? 1. Swipe down the watch home page to find the Bluetooth marker and open it. 2. Go to your phone's Settings, turn on Bluetooth, find the "T M Audio" option, and click Connect. 3. Wake up your watch, enter phone number for calling.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Surprisingly Great Gadget for the Price
reviews.reviewText: Not really a smart watch person but thought to give a try to a reasonable price before purchasing any branded expensive watch.Some cool features as advertised.1. The watch comes with two bands. The bands are adjustable and can fit anyone easily. It also comes with two screen protectors which is impressive.2. Easy to setup and connect with a phone. The message and call feature is super convenient and my favourite.3. Great metal frame gives a sturdy and stylish look.4. Battery life is great, initially i am not using it a lot but it lasts few days and charges super fast.5. There are multiple fitness related features as well, the one i am impressed with is calculating the heart rate which is a great tool for elders to monitor continuously.6. There are several options to select dial display, means you can a new watch everyday with different styles.I am really impressed with all the features and functions for such price as a new user for a smart watch.

reviews.reviewText: Yes this is a good smart watch but to start of as I have gave it 4 star ⭐ then to give it five stars is for one when I receive the order from my Amazon hub locker my package box was cut open with a blade and put upside down as I go to receive it my watch almost felt out of the delivery box I'm very disappointed with that kind of service for one and then after I get my smart watch home I try to charge it and it wasn't working I first thought it was the Wall USB outlet but still wasn't working even so I have tried a few of them and still nothing until I tried the magnetic charger from the second smart watch and then this smart watch started charging that's when I noticed the cable magnetic charger that came with this watch was defective and the second thing about this smart watch is that as you see in my pictures the matel wrist band it supposed to come with a tool in the box and that wasn't in my box not at all and plus the the wrist band didn't come with the pins either.And the most thing I'm disappointed about this smart watch is the speaker 🔊 is so so low you can't not hear it not on phone calls or music 🎶 as the watch works well but speaker sounds so low you have to put it right on ur ear 👂 come paired with the other smart watch I have the speaker is loud so I'm quite surprised so many people giving good reviews to this when I got the bad hand out this service I'm very disappointed for one bad experience with the the delivery.Bad experience with the missing items in the package.Bad experience with a defective magnetic charger.And needs improvement on the speaker.Otherwise good smart watch.Update: now I'm upset as the watch has died on me the screen started acting wierd and then it started flickering like crazy then as I cut it off
